{"tid":1593621,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"自由起義，抗共，不反華 新slogan?","createTime":"2019-09-25T06:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T09:52:02.000Z","uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64369598d8ba7490ebb3f42cd2b1c91237cdf7fe","tid":1593621,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>林鄭 不入流BOSS</strong><br />\n<strong>警黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>垃圾 BOSS</strong></span></strong><br />\n射人先射馬，擒賊先擒王，要打當然不可忘記<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>終極BOSS</strong></span></span> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Evil 共產黨</span></span></strong><br />\n各位有冇好的slogan 建議，為我們Evil 的共產黨而量身定做<br />\n以下是網路上有出現過的字眼:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">自由起義，抗共，不反華</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">信共產黨，傻的嗎</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共產黨不等於中國，佢只係漫長歷史中的其中之一的政權。還要是沒有認受性，只會用謊言跟暴力作手段的流氓政權<br />\n若沒時間去看完《暴政》一書，可以看立場簡介了的內容﹕<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%A8%E8%BF%91-%E5%86%8D%E8%AE%80%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E5%80%8B%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%95%99%E8%A8%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2587%25A8%25E8%25BF%2591-%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25AE%2580%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%25A8%2593%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9JLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=bf039527\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2587%25A8%25E8%25BF%2591-%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25AE%2580%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%25A8%2593%2F&h=b11a4ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%A8%E8%BF%91-%E5%86%8D%E8%AE%80%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E5%80%8B%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%95%99%E8%A8%93/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4384c16eec2049451ec3670f55bb8bcf10ceaf24","tid":1593621,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"20"},{"pid":"077d22f1c87304f4f7d255a8334c31ea83415a68","tid":1593621,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:07:48.000Z","msg":"19"},{"pid":"11e3f82d51acc4e5f08b1b3136feaddd3c1f05b1","tid":1593621,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"929929929<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc7d648e4042572dc2659ee10f24b517bf5d57a","tid":1593621,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:07:59.000Z","msg":"18"},{"pid":"4ca9ed07348d9ee6a863ea8d67485591ae73c858","tid":1593621,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"17"},{"pid":"b153818af9673bfa16e2abe4de5c698e9bff4b3e","tid":1593621,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:08:32.000Z","msg":"16"},{"pid":"4ba6675848afeb317ce589d0dd2a4e6556a32868","tid":1593621,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"15"},{"pid":"3df9cb8dfdee124c6820488d60c7db1662dedd6d","tid":1593621,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25